* streaming
* checksums
* cookies
* reader concurrency
* preallocation
* deletion
* compaction

write(Name, Fun)

Fun produces;
{ok, Bin}
eof
{error, Reason}

== Preallocation ==

* Extend to prealloc size on creation using fallocate/2
* Eof tracked in header.
* clean flag written to header on clean close.
* if !clean, start at Eof and skip over all entries to real Eof, write down new Eof.
